Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,莉丝妲 你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快开门!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,师傅!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看、看来我也会被扔进去呢
